main event: An unidentified flying object was tracked on radar and visually observed in Madison, Wisconsin on 21 SEP 51.
interesting points: The object was observed on ground radar as well as visually from the ground,Objects appeared to be on a collision course before veering off,The movements of the objects indicated they were under intelligent control,No known aircraft were reported in the area at the time of the sighting,The sighting lasted for about 5 minutes.
